{"type": "article", "id": 19373, "title": "2015年都有哪些好设计？Wallpaper 年度榜单出炉", "description": "欢迎浏览 2015 年度各个领域的好设计。", "date": "2015-12-21T07:05:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5281, "name": "Wallpaper"}, {"id": 20686, "name": "2015年度设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 272, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122821AWUapRSKQjwmLe9c.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t年末了，<span>wallpaper </span>网站做了 <a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/design-awards/2016#138344\" target=\"_blank\">“<span>2015 Design Award</span>” 评选</a>，这评选做得挺大，有最佳城市、最佳新酒店、最佳新餐厅、最佳公共建筑、最佳私宅、最佳男装<span>/</span>女装，及最佳产品设计等奖项。终选名单将在 <span>1 </span>月 <span>14 </span>日评出，先看看候选的好设计都有哪些吧！<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t最佳本土设计\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122752bwVGg8J1Y3vNUh0o.jpg\" title=\"‘Axor One’ control panel, by Barber &amp; Osgerby, for Axor\" alt=\"‘Axor One’ control panel, by Barber &amp; Osgerby, for Axor\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>‘Axor One’ control panel, by Barber &amp; Osgerby, for Axor</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是一个简单的淋浴控制界面，是设计机构 <a href=\"http://barberosgerby.com\" target=\"_blank\">Barber &amp; Osgerby </a>为品牌<a href=\"http://one.axor-design.com/de\" target=\"_blank\"> Axor</a> 设计的。通过这个小小的界面，人们可以控制花洒和浴缸。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071227535Dk8nXmCfNVvxKpt.jpg\" title=\"‘Serif’ TV, by Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec, for Samsung\" alt=\"‘Serif’ TV, by Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec, for Samsung\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>‘Serif’ TV, by Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec, for Samsung</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是设计机构 <span><a href=\"http://www.bouroullec.com\" target=\"_blank\">Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec </a></span>为<span> <a href=\"http://www.bouroullec.com\" target=\"_blank\">Samsung</a> </span>设计的电视。猛地一看，它像是 <span>1950 </span>年代的产品，有着古旧的支撑腿和外型。复古的外观让我们重新思考电视在生活中扮演的角色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122753mHdftUQsoguMEFLY.jpg\" title=\"Kettle and toaster, by Naoto Fukasawa, for Muji\" alt=\"Kettle and toaster, by Naoto Fukasawa, for Muji\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Kettle and toaster, by Naoto Fukasawa, for Muji</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t上图是深泽直人为<a href=\"http://www.muji.com\" target=\"_blank\">无印良品</a>设计的水壶和烤面包机。纯白、简洁，延续了 MUJI 一贯的风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071227537l2dW4i1NrMmbQDB.jpg\" title=\"‘Pan 999’ pots and pans, by Tobia Scarpa, for San Lorenzo Best domestic design\" alt=\"‘Pan 999’ pots and pans, by Tobia Scarpa, for San Lorenzo Best domestic design\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>‘Pan 999’ pots and pans, by Tobia Scarpa, for San Lorenzo </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t银器可以杀菌，意大利银器设计师<a href=\"http://www.pan999.it\" target=\"_blank\"> San Lorenzo</a> 设计了这组银器，它内部为银，外部为铁。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122754KoMUzQPCixE7WAgX.jpg\" title=\"BeoSound Moment, by Bang &amp; Olufsen\" alt=\"BeoSound Moment, by Bang &amp; Olufsen\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>BeoSound Moment, by Bang &amp; Olufsen</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>BeoSound Moment </span>是智能的无线音乐系统，可以将音乐与流媒体服务合于一体。只需指尖轻触木质面板，其他就可以交给<span> BeoSound Moment </span>完成。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>年度设计师</span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;\"> </span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:transparent;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122754PkiUCdNhLwj6x5ac.jpg\" title=\"Nendo\" alt=\"Nendo\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">Nendo\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t我们曾经在网站上多次介绍过 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/release/2015/\" target=\"_blank\">Nendo</a>，“Nendo” 是日本设计师佐藤大于 2002 年成立的设计工作室，它的设计领域广泛，于东京及意大利米兰皆设有据点。佐藤大 1977 年出生于加拿大，2002 年在日本早稻田大学获得了建筑学的硕士学位，同年在东京创建了名为 Nendo 。Nendo 以勤奋著名，在国际设计领域都极为知名。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122755kE8LSOQ9ZamBNJ4K.jpg\" title=\"Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec\" alt=\"Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec\" data-ratio=\"1.42598187\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.bouroullec.com\" target=\"_blank\">Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tRonan 和 Erwan 是一对法国兄弟，他们都出生于法国坎佩尔，哥哥出生于 1971 年，弟弟出生于 1976 年。他们都学习设计专业，1999 年共同创立了设计工作室。2003 年，他们凭借 “joyn” 办公系统的设计一炮而红。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122755dS43oWVxw2Xtk16R.jpg\" title=\"Max Lamb\" alt=\"Max Lamb\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Max Lamb</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.maxlamb.org\" target=\"_blank\">Max Lamb </a>是成立于 2007 年的伦敦设计工作室，他们主要从事家具设计。今年早些时候，他们在米兰家具展上展出了设计过的 41 把椅子，设计充满了幽默感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071227568TJygxlq0N5Q4W1h.jpg\" title=\"Aldo Bakker\" alt=\"Aldo Bakker\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.aldobakker.com\" target=\"_blank\">Aldo Bakker</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t陶瓷设计师 Aldo Bakker <span style=\"text-align:left;\">是荷兰人，他</span>的瓷器设计相当巧妙，常常超脱常规的设计思维。<span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122756bLN3oeD5fyEnBPZq.jpg\" title=\"Barber &amp; Osgerby\" alt=\"Barber &amp; Osgerby\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Barber &amp; Osgerby</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家工作室的主设计师是 Edward Barber 和 Jay Osgerby。他们的工作室位于伦敦东区，1997 年，二人设计的第一件家具 Loop 矮桌在伦敦设计展 Wallpaper 的展台上被 Giulio Cappellini 一眼相中, 并由 Cappellini 投入生产。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>年度新餐厅</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122756mvCydkqJcaVzKMns.jpg\" title=\"Usine, Stockholm\" alt=\"Usine, Stockholm\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.usine.se\" target=\"_blank\">Usine</a>, Stockholm</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家餐厅是由一家香肠厂改造的，它占地面积超过 2000 平方米，混凝土地板和照明系统很出彩。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122757iHhOzD1LUbJXnTFa.jpg\" title=\"Juana La Loca, Bogotá\" alt=\"Juana La Loca, Bogotá\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Juana La Loca, Bogotá</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家餐厅是由 <span>Isay Weinfeld </span>设计的，是一个由木材包裹的餐厅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122758Pwkrbpua2x5MftjY.jpg\" title=\"Spring, London\" alt=\"Spring, London\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Spring, London</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是澳大利亚厨师 <span>Skye Gyngell </span>的餐厅，这是一个平静、明亮的餐饮空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122758bdRFa1G6tx7uC3Hy.jpg\" title=\"Raw, Taipei\" alt=\"Raw, Taipei\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Raw, Taipei</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>这家台湾餐厅有着定制家具和微妙灯光，亦当选年度候选餐厅。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122759MCA0kORhJX7wVT3E.jpg\" title=\"Alancha, Istanbul\" alt=\"Alancha, Istanbul\" data-ratio=\"1.27567568\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Alancha, Istanbul</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家餐厅使用新鲜的食材，提供土耳其特色食品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳新酒店</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122759V3UZ6gPtaun4EmrT.jpg\" title=\"Aman, Tokyo\" alt=\"Aman, Tokyo\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.amantokyo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Aman</a>, Tokyo</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家酒店的内室是由 Kerry Hill Architects 设计的，他们使用了樟脑木、纸和石头等材质，辅之以当代日本纺织品。这家酒店里还有一家传统汉方医学图书馆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228010Q4XwZU6uoMhHI3y.jpg\" title=\"Chicago Athletic Association, Chicago\" alt=\"Chicago Athletic Association, Chicago\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.chicagoathletichotel.com\" target=\"_blank\">Chicago Athletic Association,</a> Chicago</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这幢建筑由设计于 1893 年，它曾是芝加哥的体育中心，后被改造成 241 间客房的酒店。很多元素被保留了下来，包括彩色玻璃窗和宏伟的大理石楼梯。现在酒店有屋顶餐厅、露天阳台、汉堡店、威士忌酒吧、互动游戏室和 24 小时开放的健身设施。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122801AtJVBqQYzuHvh1ge.jpg\" title=\"Blossom Hill Inn, Hangzhou\" alt=\"Blossom Hill Inn, Hangzhou\" data-ratio=\"1.14563107\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Blossom Hill Inn, Hangzhou</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t杭州西溪花间堂位于杭州西溪国家湿地公园，酒店设有一个室外游泳池、spa中心和一间餐厅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122802uJsXx5riGoN8klOC.jpg\" title=\"Les Bains, Paris\" alt=\"Les Bains, Paris\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.lesbains-paris.com\" target=\"_blank\">Les Bains</a>, Paris</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t上图中的巴黎酒店以泳池和水疗中心著名。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228031aZXlkzU2nwiCH9Y.jpg\" title=\"Edition, Miami Beach\" alt=\"Edition, Miami Beach\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.editionhotels.com\" target=\"_blank\">Edition,</a> Miami Beach</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家酒店有 323 个房间，还有广阔的海滨和露天电影院。\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳新私宅</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122804mV25Bc8FlUJ4EutM.jpg\" title=\"Villa Moelven, Sweden, by Widjedal Racki\" alt=\"Villa Moelven, Sweden, by Widjedal Racki\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Villa Moelven, Sweden, by Widjedal Racki</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228043u4FyZrm9U80Dqzd.jpg\" title=\"Grigio, Japan, by Apollo Architects &amp; Associates\" alt=\"Grigio, Japan, by Apollo Architects &amp; Associates\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Grigio, Japan, by Apollo Architects &amp; Associates</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122804akMuBwTKi8HCoUL2.jpg\" title=\"Lattice House, India, by Sameep Padora &amp; Associates\" alt=\"Lattice House, India, by Sameep Padora &amp; Associates\" data-ratio=\"1.19191919\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Lattice House, India, by Sameep Padora &amp; Associates</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228053y9cJQ8glFRdaCbn.jpg\" title=\"Concrete House, Australia, by Matt Gibson\" alt=\"Concrete House, Australia, by Matt Gibson\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Concrete House, Australia, by Matt Gibson</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122805KAzJLcrkvhYIM7Od.jpg\" title=\"Berkshire Residence, US, by Tom Kundig/Olson Kundig\" alt=\"Berkshire Residence, US, by Tom Kundig/Olson Kundig\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Berkshire Residence, US, by Tom Kundig/Olson Kundig</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳公共建筑   </span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122806Nka4B9LwMCb3G7uv.jpg\" title=\"Whitney Museum, US, by Renzo Piano Building Workshop\" alt=\"Whitney Museum, US, by Renzo Piano Building Workshop\" data-ratio=\"0.74947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Whitney Museum, US, by Renzo Piano Building Workshop</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是位于麦迪逊大道的新博物馆。它共有 9 层，包括画廊、\r\n教育中心、剧院、实验室、图书馆及阅览室。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122807096bHsnLgmFiaRvu.jpg\" title=\"The Broad, US, by Diller Scofidio + Renfro\" alt=\"The Broad, US, by Diller Scofidio + Renfro\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>The Broad, US, by Diller Scofidio + </span>Benfro\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>这是 LA 新的宽阔的博物馆，它最大的特点是幕墙外数百个蜂窝状的开口。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122807Vq25YgwXvkZdefOA.jpg\" title=\"Fondazione Prada, Italy, by OMA\" alt=\"Fondazione Prada, Italy, by OMA\" data-ratio=\"0.71368421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.fondazioneprada.org\" target=\"_blank\">Fondazione Prada</a>, Italy, by OMA</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是 OMA 设计的意大利普拉达基金会，它尽力做到了新和旧的结合。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122808OcJa4SBP8GYLqklW.jpg\" title=\"Learning Hub, Singapore, by Heatherwick Studio\" alt=\"Learning Hub, Singapore, by Heatherwick Studio\" data-ratio=\"0.70631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.heatherwick.com\" target=\"_blank\">Learning Hub</a>, Singapore, by Heatherwick Studio</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t上图中的建筑群是新加坡南洋科技大学的一部分。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228080g2C7KpEzIRqbStO.jpg\" title=\"Folk Art Museum for China Academy of Arts, China, by Kengo \" alt=\"Folk Art Museum for China Academy of Arts, China, by Kengo \" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.kkaa.co.jp\" target=\"_blank\">Folk Art Museum for China Academy of Arts</a>, China, by Kengo </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t日本隈研吾建筑事务所设计了中国美术学院民艺馆，大量的弧形瓦片覆盖了人字形屋顶，看上去就像一个小村庄。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳城市    </span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122809BSfuzo0J2cMrFNA7.jpg\" title=\"Beirut\" alt=\"Beirut\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">黎巴嫩港口贝鲁特（<span>Beirut） </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122809R5F3rT8DGSenaOsZ.jpg\" title=\"迈阿密\" alt=\"迈阿密\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>迈阿密</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122809LPo2iUX9hRsT1Hu8.jpg\" title=\"哥本哈根\" alt=\"哥本哈根\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>哥本哈根</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122810mHa2eu514E6zSfOZ.jpg\" title=\"洛杉矶\" alt=\"洛杉矶\" data-ratio=\"0.60740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洛杉矶</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122811iPfpWZbGwhoOLmkU.jpg\" title=\"台北\" alt=\"台北\" data-ratio=\"0.61666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>台北</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳女装</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122811dkJtluUpNomWQZGT.jpg\" title=\"Gucci\" alt=\"Gucci\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Gucci </span>(A/W 2015)<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122812WRPqMIe0f5gNicpl.jpg\" title=\"Céline\" alt=\"Céline\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Céline<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122812whRaubeG6m8AYWkp.jpg\" title=\"Marni\" alt=\"Marni\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Marni<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122813xFC4IaKlQJyR7ZBE.jpg\" title=\"Comme des Garçons\" alt=\"Comme des Garçons\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Comme des Garçons<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228133wcUW9IMxu86mjhR.jpg\" title=\"Louis Vuitton\" alt=\"Louis Vuitton\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Louis Vuitton<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳男装</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122813nuGZABgLpoq4vi8I.jpg\" title=\"Ermenegildo Zegna Couture\" alt=\"Ermenegildo Zegna Couture\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Ermenegildo Zegna Couture<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122814klcUQ9VBMEJOAKeb.jpg\" title=\"Comme des Garçons\" alt=\"Comme des Garçons\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Comme des Garçons<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122815nkGX0td6FeIAZ7sJ.jpg\" title=\"Caruso\" alt=\"Caruso\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Caruso<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122815nRz7XrQTvH3ok1KB.jpg\" title=\"Prada\" alt=\"Prada\" data-ratio=\"1.49789474\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Prada<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122816hLsezrqB4UmEwFKk.jpg\" title=\"Junya Watanabe\" alt=\"Junya Watanabe\" data-ratio=\"1.4984127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Junya Watanabe<span style=\"text-align:center;\">(A/W 2015)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span>最佳产品设计</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122816vsXtVB8Z2Pbn1KmQ.jpg\" title=\"Natural pigment nail polish, by Buly 1803\" alt=\"Natural pigment nail polish, by Buly 1803\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.buly1803.com\" target=\"_blank\">Natural pigment nail polish</a>, by Buly 1803</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这是一款无化学成分的无毒指甲油，由压碎的海贝壳和天然色素构成，一系列共有<span> 15 </span>个颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122817y34MpAYdNq6lzfbw.jpg\" title=\"Misoka•ISM toothbrush, by Misoka\" alt=\"Misoka•ISM toothbrush, by Misoka\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.misoka.jp\" target=\"_blank\">Misoka</a>•ISM toothbrush, by Misoka</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这种牙刷可能看起来相当传统，但它的刚毛很特别，有纳米涂层。当他们浸在水中的时候，就会被激活。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122817Xp6ZJt1RuMSPBkqD.jpg\" title=\"Haircare range, by Susanne Kaufmann\" alt=\"Haircare range, by Susanne Kaufmann\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://www.susannekaufmann.com\" target=\"_blank\">Haircare range</a>, by Susanne Kaufmann</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这个奥地利的护发品牌一直是 wallpaper 的心头好。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122818ygfOezJuYd5haclq.jpg\" title=\"Misia, by Chanel\" alt=\"Misia, by Chanel\" data-ratio=\"1.10280374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Misia, by Chanel</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t香奈儿的 <span>Les Exclusifs </span>也上榜了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122818qX1ljh8fieQbyUmG.jpg\" title=\"Y-S.C.1 beard oil, by Ya-sin Chahimi\" alt=\"Y-S.C.1 beard oil, by Ya-sin Chahimi\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Y-S.C.1 beard oil, by Ya-sin Chahimi</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228181LBudNxTUniItVbF.jpg\" title=\"Apple Watch Hermès, by Apple and Hermès\" alt=\"Apple Watch Hermès, by Apple and Hermès\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Apple Watch Hermès, by Apple and Hermès</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122819mzH3oDrPTJcxg2RI.jpg\" title=\"Drinkable perfumes, by Kille Enna\" alt=\"Drinkable perfumes, by Kille Enna\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Drinkable perfumes, by Kille Enna</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071228197uakFNZ2PAimxvhd.jpg\" title=\"MP 01 mobile phone, by Jasper Morrison and Punkt\" alt=\"MP 01 mobile phone, by Jasper Morrison and Punkt\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>MP 01 mobile phone, by Jasper Morrison and Punkt</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122820l3BJU8xZLP7AFsXe.jpg\" title=\"Jean Prouvé’s 6x6 Demountable House, by Rogers Stirk Harbour + Partners and Patrick Seguin\" alt=\"Jean Prouvé’s 6x6 Demountable House, by Rogers Stirk Harbour + Partners and Patrick Seguin\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Jean Prouvé’s 6x6 Demountable House, by Rogers Stirk Harbour + Partners and Patrick Seguin</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122820rFlmy0P4gRw7XthN.jpg\" title=\"Enjoy online gadget store, by Ron Johnson\" alt=\"Enjoy online gadget store, by Ron Johnson\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Enjoy online gadget store, by Ron Johnson</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/design-awards/2016#138314\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}